      • addDeclassificationTransition

        public boolean addDeclassificationTransition(java.lang.String transitionName)
        Adds a declassification transition with the given name to the IF-Net.
        Transitions names have to be unique. In case the net already contains a transition with the given name, no transition is added to the net.
        参数:
        transitionName - The name for the declassification transition.
        返回:
        true if the transition was successfully added to the net;
        false otherwise.
        抛出:
        de.invation.code.toval.validate.ParameterException - If the transition name is null.
